# Java String Programs

## 📌 Project Overview

This repository contains various Java programs based on **String manipulation and operations**. These programs help beginners understand how strings work in Java and improve problem-solving skills using built-in String methods.

## 📂 Programs Included

* Reverse a String
* Check Palindrome String


## 🛠 Technologies Used

* Java
* Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)
* String Class Methods

## 🚀 Concepts Covered

### String Methods

* `length()`
* `charAt()`
* `substring()`
* `equals()`
* `equalsIgnoreCase()`
* `compareTo()`
* `contains()`
* `replace()`
* `toUpperCase()`
* `toLowerCase()`
* `trim()`
* `split()`

## ▶️ Sample Program

### Reverse a String

```java
public class ReverseString {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str = "Java";
        String reverse = "";

        for(int i = str.length()-1; i >= 0; i--) {
            reverse += str.charAt(i);
        }

        System.out.println("Reversed String: " + reverse);
    }
}
```

### Output

```text
Reversed String: avaJ
```

